---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import RevealText from '@/components/RevealText.astro';
---

<Base title="Fees | WORK Labs">
  <div class="section-shell">
    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">01 Fee$</span><span>Terms of Business</span></div>
      <RevealText as="h1" variant="title" class="route-title">Fee Structure</RevealText>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">02 Core Terms</span><span>Simple Agreement</span></div>
      <div class="data-grid">
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">Scope</p><p class="text-sm mt-2">Multi-directional strategic and creative thinking with scheduled concept reviews every 6-8 weeks.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">Structure</p><p class="text-sm mt-2">Monthly project fee for a 12-month term; out-of-scope work requires prior approval.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">Rights</p><p class="text-sm mt-2">Client owns adopted and paid-for assets. Unused materials remain with WORK.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">Ops</p><p class="text-sm mt-2">Out-of-pocket expenses capped without approval; invoice terms net 21 days.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">Legal</p><p class="text-sm mt-2">Reasonable confidentiality and non-compete agreements accepted.</p></article>
        <article class="data-cell"><p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate">Principle</p><p class="text-sm mt-2">Streamline over over-processing: fewer layers, faster clarity, stronger execution.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">03 Market Reality</span><span>Agency Cost Gravity</span></div>
        <p class="text-sm">The source document outlines 35 separate line items a typical agency may charge to create and launch a startup brand, often totaling well beyond early-stage budgets.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="kicker"><span class="section-number">04 Position</span><span>WORK Approach</span></div>
        <p class="text-sm">Integrated senior thinking and execution infrastructure reduces overhead fragmentation and keeps decisions tied to business outcomes.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions mt-6">
          <a href="/launchpad" data-transition-link class="button cta-secondary">View Launchpad</a>
          <a href="/contact" data-transition-link class="button cta-primary">Discuss Scope</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
